Deji Elumoye in Abuja The Senate Deputy Minority Leader, Senator Emmanuel Bwacha (PDP Taraba), has defected to the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC). His defection was made public on Thursday when the Chairman of APC National Caretaker Committee and Governor of Yobe State, Mai Mala Buni, presented him to President Muhammadu Buhari at the State House, Abuja. President Buhari, in the presence of his Chief of Staff, Prof. Ibrahim Gambari, welcomed the ranking senator and latest entrant into the party. Details laterâ€¦